---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead
			title={`About — ${SITE_TITLE}`}
			description="Gareth Winter. Cyclist, creative leader, former Creative Director at Team Sky."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<main class="about-main">
			<div class="container">
				<header class="about-head">
					<p class="label about-kicker">About</p>
					<h1 class="about-title">Gareth Winter</h1>
				</header>

				<article class="prose about-prose">
					<figure class="pull-quote">
						<blockquote>
							<p>
								"Live your life while you have it. Life is a splendid gift —
								there is nothing small about it."
							</p>
						</blockquote>
						<figcaption class="quote-caption">— Branda Winter</figcaption>
					</figure>

					<p>
						I grew up with stories like that. Stories about grit, service, pride in
						craft, and doing things properly, even when no one is watching. Cycling
						was never just a sport in my family. It was culture. It was character. It
						was a way of measuring yourself honestly.
					</p>

					<p>That belief still shapes everything I do.</p>

					<h2>Cycling Was the Classroom</h2>
					<p>
						The bike is an honest mirror. It rewards patience, exposes ego, and
						punishes sloppy details. Do the work, get the result. Skip the work, pay
						for it.
					</p>

					<h2>Work, at the Highest Level</h2>
					<p>
						I've spent over a decade inside elite performance environments. Former
						Creative Director at Team Sky, working alongside Olympic champions and
						Grand Tour winners. Contributor to systems that delivered Olympic gold
						medals, Tour de France and Giro d'Italia victories.
					</p>

					<p>
						Now leading creative strategy and performance systems at Mindvalley,
						focused on human optimisation and transformation at global scale.
					</p>

					<p class="about-signoff">
						Cyclist. Creative leader. Student of marginal gains.
					</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.about-main {
		padding-top: var(--s-9);
		padding-bottom: var(--s-10);
	}

	.about-head {
		max-width: var(--measure);
		margin: 0 auto var(--s-8);
	}

	.about-kicker {
		margin-bottom: var(--s-4);
	}

	.about-title {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, var(--text-4xl));
		font-weight: 300;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		line-height: 1.05;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.about-prose {
		max-width: var(--measure);
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* Pull quote — magazine centrepiece */
	.pull-quote {
		margin: 0 0 var(--s-8);
		padding: var(--s-7) 0;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.pull-quote blockquote {
		margin: 0 0 var(--s-3);
		padding: 0;
		border: none;
		background: none;
	}

	.pull-quote blockquote p {
		font-family: var(--font-serif);
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, var(--text-2xl));
		font-weight: 300;
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.35;
		color: var(--ink);
		margin: 0;
	}

	.quote-caption {
		display: block;
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		color: var(--muted);
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}

	.about-signoff {
		font-size: var(--text-sm);
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--muted);
		margin-top: var(--s-7);
	}
</style>
